    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="letter">
                <pb n="1" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_1841_05_08_page01.jpg"/>
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#North-Audley-Street-1_ENK"/>1 North Audley Street
                        <date when="1841-05-08">May 8. 1841</date></dateline>
                    <salute><choice><orig>D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi></orig><reg>Dear</reg></choice>. Sir</salute>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <persName ref="./Personography.xml#MoorX1">M<hi rend="superscript">rs</hi>. Moore</persName> was with me<lb/>
                    this morning waiting for<lb/>
                    your answer - But hearing<lb/>
                    you were not at home when<lb/>
                    my messenger was with you<lb/>
                    she could no longer stay here<lb/>
                    She tells me she will drive<lb/>
                    to your house herself and<lb/>
                    learn your ultimatum<lb/>
                </p>
                <p>
                    I <unclear>think</unclear>, as I know she does,<lb/>
                    that you may be the publisher<lb/>
                    of her <persName ref="./Personography.xml#MoorG1">husbands</persName> <choice><orig><unclear>M<hi rend="superscript">s</hi>.</unclear></orig><reg>manuscript</reg></choice>, as that<lb/>
                    would be most creditable<lb/>
                    to his literary fame, <hi rend="underline">which</hi><lb/>
                    <hi rend="underline">is her Object</hi> - But whatever<lb/>
                    your determination may be<lb/>
                    Give her now a decided answer<lb/>
                    I pray you, and let her have<lb/>
                    this <choice><orig><unclear>M<hi rend="superscript"><hi rend="underline">s</hi></hi></unclear></orig><reg>manuscript</reg></choice> if you decline <choice><orig>publish</orig><reg>publishing</reg></choice><lb/>
                    ing<lb/>
                </p>
                <pb n="2" facs="Edgeworth_NLS_42180_1841_05_08_page02.jpg"/>
                <p>
                    if that she may make another<lb/>
                    arrangement with <hi rend="underline">next best</hi><lb/>
                    <hi rend="underline">publisher</hi> before <hi rend="underline">she leaves</hi><lb/>
                    <placeName ref="./Placeography.xml#Edgeworthstown_IE"><hi rend="underline">Town</hi></placeName> - on Monday I believe<lb/>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    Yours sincerely<lb/>
                    <persName ref="./Personography.xml#EdgeM1">Maria Edgeworth</persName><lb/>
                    Saturday April 8<hi rend="superscript"><hi rend="underline">th</hi></hi> 1841<lb/>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
